original_title: The High Kings - Live In Dublin
overview: The High King’s ‘Live In Dublin’ DVD was released in 2007 and features the band performing in front of a hugely appreciative Dublin audience at The Helix venue. The concert features many of the songs that the band has become known for performing live including ‘The Rocky Road To Dublin’ and ‘The Auld Triangle’ along with many other favourites. This DVD is unrated and all region.  1. The Rocky Road To Dublin2. The Black Velvet Band 3.Jimmy Murphy 4. The Wild Rover 5. Paddy’s Green Shamrock Shore 6. Galway To Graceland 7. The Little Beggarman 8. The Beggarman Jig 9. Bodhrán Solo 10. Dance At The Crossroads 11. The Holy Ground 12. Will Ye Go Lassie, Go? 13. Fields of Glory 14. Marie’s Wedding 15.The Auld Triangle 16. Ar Eirinn Ni Neosainn Cé Hí 17. Phil The Fluther’s Ball 18. The Parting Glass
